        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="解决Plugin-load-failed-hexo-renderer-kramed及Plugin-load-failed-hexo-tag-aplayer问题"><a href="#解决Plugin-load-failed-hexo-renderer-kramed及Plugin-load-failed-hexo-tag-aplayer问题" class="headerlink" title="解决Plugin load failed: hexo-renderer-kramed及Plugin load failed: hexo-tag-aplayer问题"></a>解决Plugin load failed: hexo-renderer-kramed及Plugin load failed: hexo-tag-aplayer问题</h3><h4 id="报错原因："><a href="#报错原因：" class="headerlink" title="报错原因："></a>报错原因：</h4><p>本地hexo博客工程文件的路径名中有修改</p><p>解决办法：</p><p>卸载，重装</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm uninstall hexo-renderer-kramed --save</span><br><span class="line">cnpm uninstall hexo-tag-aplayer --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-renderer-kramed --save</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-tag-aplayer --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> web前端 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Hexo </tag>
            
            <tag> error </tag>
            
